# PART 5 — CONTACT, NAVIGATION & TRUST ELEMENTS

Kamiyon Studio Website Specification v2.0

> **Note:** v1 has no separate Awards, Partners, Team, or Testimonials pages. Trust elements are distributed across Home, About, and Press. This document defines Contact, global navigation, footer, and where trust content lives.

---

## TRUST CONTENT DISTRIBUTION

| Trust element | Location in v1 |
| --- | --- |
| Client / partner logos | Home → Clients / Partners section |
| Awards highlight | Home → Awards section |
| Full press / media assets | Press kit → `/pres` |
| Team profiles | About → Team section |
| Testimonials | **Not in v1** — add when real quotes exist in canon |
| Studio stats | Home trust row (optional) + About stats row (optional) |

**Rule:** Never fabricate logos, awards, or testimonials. Use labeled placeholders.

---

## CONTACT PAGE (`/contact`)

### Objective

Primary conversion page. Make it effortless to reach Kamiyon.

### Page flow

```
Hero
    ↓
Google Form embed
    ↓
Direct contact methods (mailto + socials)
    ↓
FAQ (optional)
    ↓
Sidebar info (optional on desktop)
```

---

### Hero

- Headline: "Let's build something together."
- Supporting: 1–2 sentences welcoming project inquiries of any stage
- Tone: warm, professional, concise

---

### Google Form embed

**Primary contact mechanism for v1.**

| Property | Spec |
| --- | --- |
| Implementation | iframe or Google Forms embed |
| Config | `NEXT_PUBLIC_CONTACT_FORM_URL` environment variable |
| Width | Full content width, max ~720px centered |
| Height | Responsive; min ~600px or auto-resize if supported |
| Styling | Surrounded by white card with soft shadow to match site |

**Suggested form fields (configure in Google Form):**

- Name
- Company (optional)
- Email
- Project type (dropdown: Games, Design, Illustration, Branding, 3D & Motion, Web, Other)
- Budget range (dropdown, optional)
- Timeline (dropdown, optional)
- Project description (long text)

**Explicitly excluded:**

- Calendly or any booking widget
- Custom backend form handler / API route for v1
- File upload (unless added to Google Form directly)

---

### Direct contact methods

Display below or beside the form as prominent cards or link row:

| Method | Implementation |
| --- | --- |
| Email | `mailto:` link from canon |
| LinkedIn | External URL from canon |
| Facebook | External URL from canon |

- Each: icon, label, short description (e.g. "We respond within 1–2 business days")
- Placeholder `#` with "Coming soon" label if URL not in canon yet

---

### FAQ (optional, 3–5 items)

Accordion on contact page only:

- How quickly do you respond?
- Do you sign NDAs?
- Do you work internationally?
- Can you help refine an early idea?
- Do you work with startups?

Source answers from `docs/services/consultation-process.md` and `docs/ai/faq.md` where available.

---

### Sidebar (desktop)

Optional right column:

| Item | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Location | Biñan City, Laguna, Philippines |
| Founded | 2024 |
| Email | mailto link |
