### Success / error states

Google Form handles submission natively. No custom success page required for v1.

If a custom thank-you route is added later:

- Kami-chan celebrating illustration
- Message: "Thanks for reaching out! We'll review your project within 1–2 business days."
- Buttons: Back to Home, Explore Portfolio

