## GLOBAL NAVIGATION

### Desktop

```
[Logo]     Portfolio   News   About   Press   Contact     [Discuss Your Project]
```

| Link | Route |
| --- | --- |
| Logo | `/` |
| Portfolio | `/portfolio` |
| News | `/news` |
| About | `/about` |
| Press | `/pres` |
| Contact | `/contact` |
| CTA button | `/contact` |

### Mobile

- Hamburger icon opens full-screen or slide drawer
- All links + CTA button inside drawer
- Close on navigation

### Active state

- Current page: pink underline or pink text
- CTA button: always pink filled pill

### Behavior

- Sticky top
- White background + subtle shadow after scroll
- Height: 72–88px
- Logo never smaller than readable minimum

